Sentencas: Sr- and Mg-doped lanthanum gallate which exhibits high ionic conductivity was synthesized by a citrate method using industrial raw materials.
Titulo: Preparation of La1-xSrxGa0.8Mg0.2O3-δ electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell by citrate method using industrial raw materials

Sentencas: analysis revealed that the powder by a citrate method was single-phase.
Titulo: Preparation of La1-xSrxGa0.8Mg0.2O3-δ electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell by citrate method using industrial raw materials

Sentencas: Electron probe micro analysis (EPMA) showed that the sintered body which was formed by synthesized powder by a citrate method and fired at 1723 K for 6 h had inhomogeneous texture caused by segregation of Sr and Ga elements.
Titulo: Preparation of La1-xSrxGa0.8Mg0.2O3-δ electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell by citrate method using industrial raw materials

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscope (SEM) images and densimetry revealed that the sintered body synthesized by a citrate method had high density, the sintered bodies synthesized by a citrate method had much higher oxide ion conductivity than those by a solid state reaction method.
Titulo: Preparation of La1-xSrxGa0.8Mg0.2O3-δ electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell by citrate method using industrial raw materials
